title: Cheeze drops teaser for 'Love You (Bye)' | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Cheeze drops teaser for 'Love You (Bye)' By KpopJoA 7 minutes ago 623 0 0 0 Google+ Group Cheeze has released a teaser video of their new ballad "Love You (Bye) ".
The video features a man staring at the camera as Cheeze's angelic voice is heard in the background. 
The full version of "Love You (Bye)" will be debuting on February 20. Check out the clip above! YOU MAY LIKE GET AKP IN YOUR INBOX! ..or follow allkpop to stay updated: Tags:
